{"tid":1307722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打不還手為我地爭取左咩人嘅支持？","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T05:00:47.000Z","uid":69221,"like":91,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f843658a071022374d633b778e756a72d3966735","tid":1307722,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"論點<br />\n<br />\n<em>為文宣組增加左素材，可以展示到自己弱小可憐啦<br />\n<br />\n會引到中立撚支持</em><br />\n<br />\n會因為呢件事而支持或者同情你嘅人<br />\n<br />\n本身對政治了解有幾深？<br />\n<br />\n明唔明白我哋本身面對緊制度暴力？<br />\n<br />\n今日佢同情俾人打不還手嘅巴打<br />\n<br />\n過幾日佢見到遊行有人用暴力，你估佢仲支唔支持？<br />\n<br />\n我哋需要嘅支持者係了解政治，<br />\n<br />\n同意必須破壞舊有制度從而建立新制度嘅人<br />\n<br />\n唔係一啲一知半解單純被畫面同埋口號帶風向嘅港豬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一四年雨傘革命就係充滿呢啲人<br />\n<br />\n922罷課 925圍禮賓府 926衝公民廣場<br />\n<br />\n參與嘅係咩人？全部都係本身關心政治嘅人<br />\n<br />\n當中大部份嘅人都係928見到催淚彈先出嚟<br />\n<br />\n佢哋個諗法只係唔好打學生唔好用暴力<br />\n<br />\n根本忽視左個根源，政府，黑警本身就係被合理化嘅嘅暴力<br />\n<br />\n當你嘅目標最終都係要靠暴力去達成<br />\n<br />\n咁你用示弱去吸引一班無知嘅人同情你根本係戇撚柒鳩<br />\n<br />\n最終佢哋會掉轉槍屌返你<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"bd073b66e5b7bf82b24687ff26d5f732436fffd7","tid":1307722,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296d07cda4ca88f686decfa25d503513688eec55","tid":1307722,"uid":2429,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bNFY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bNFY6E.jpg&h=0e3ff068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJqqMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJqqMr.jpg&h=d5937562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUnCgTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUnCgTg.jpg&h=4d401a96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAgxru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAgxru.jpg&h=a97e178b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"b936b698728bd203cf9f7f6d9a5b00f9ff611206","tid":1307722,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34c2b8cd6b7939ff2b486327c0fa6708d21f1c3","tid":1307722,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"留低個負皮唔出聲即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96e4e770ed57b48b14b434b027a01f8d640d558","tid":1307722,"uid":124859,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"人血鏝頭<br />\n左膠見死不救"},{"pid":"5419c1b39074281d6f6cf0fa614993b6a0ac4187","tid":1307722,"uid":394,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"200萬人上街 5條人命 係支持嘅一早歸曬邊<br />\n而家仲唔還手做沙包搏騎場派支持<br />\n好野"},{"pid":"0d90fc900c685aa2101fff1b35710284b0340024","tid":1307722,"uid":394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96e4e770ed57b48b14b434b027a01f8d640d558","tid":1307722,"uid":124859,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"人血鏝頭<br />\n左膠見死不救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f24f544717be6e167240591af9a312260ca7bb4","tid":1307722,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96e4e770ed57b48b14